WEBVTT

00:00:08.320 --> 00:00:09.400
In other words,

00:00:09.679 --> 00:00:11.679
Xin Qili didn't want his sister to recover.

00:00:11.839 --> 00:00:13.839
At least he struggled with it.

00:00:14.800 --> 00:00:15.919
His sister's medical bills,

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:17.280
he was paying them all, right?

00:00:17.800 --> 00:00:18.519
Right.

00:00:18.960 --> 00:00:19.920
He transferred money on schedule every month

00:00:19.920 --> 00:00:21.039
into his sister's account.

00:00:22.320 --> 00:00:24.359
Could the burden of those bills be why

00:00:25.120 --> 00:00:26.359
he burned

00:00:26.399 --> 00:00:28.039
the Fortune slip he prayed for her with?

00:00:30.239 --> 00:00:31.600
The complexity of human nature, Boss.

00:00:31.760 --> 00:00:34.119
What "The complexity of human nature"?

00:00:38.320 --> 00:00:39.479
Ruan Chen.

00:01:11.239 --> 00:01:12.879
Hey, what kind of driving is that?

00:01:12.959 --> 00:01:13.640
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

00:01:13.680 --> 00:01:14.560
How did you even hit me?

00:01:14.640 --> 00:01:15.959
The rear bumper's bent.

00:01:16.920 --> 00:01:18.400
A Min's guys are tailing you.

00:01:18.519 --> 00:01:19.719
Let me just give you some cash.

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:20.959
I'm rushing to work.

00:01:21.359 --> 00:01:22.120
Sorry about this.

00:02:15.680 --> 00:02:16.599
Who are you?

00:02:17.759 --> 00:02:18.719
Who would've thought,

00:02:19.000 --> 00:02:20.280
Bro Mao's fake memorial hall

00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:22.879
would come in handy so soon.

00:02:24.960 --> 00:02:26.000
Who the hell are you?

00:02:28.919 --> 00:02:32.759
Xin Qili was jailed for an Economic crime before.

00:02:34.039 --> 00:02:35.639
That company back then was called...

00:02:35.719 --> 00:02:36.759
What was it called again?

00:02:37.159 --> 00:02:38.039
Yizhan Technology.

00:02:38.159 --> 00:02:38.960
Right, right, right.

00:02:39.159 --> 00:02:40.479
Yizhan Technology.

00:02:40.560 --> 00:02:41.759
The 0301 Dismemberment Case.

00:02:42.159 --> 00:02:44.080
The victim, Tian Yong, was the boss of Yizhan Technology.

00:02:46.199 --> 00:02:48.159
Both involve Yizhan Technology,

00:02:48.680 --> 00:02:50.759
and both are dismemberment cases.

00:02:56.240 --> 00:02:58.080
Xin Qili once headed a branch

00:02:58.080 --> 00:02:58.800
of Yizhan Technology.

00:02:59.560 --> 00:03:00.719
Less than a month into the job,

00:03:00.879 --> 00:03:02.520
the company was investigated for money laundering.

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:04.439
That's what put him behind bars.

00:03:07.960 --> 00:03:09.479
But in both cases,

00:03:11.080 --> 00:03:13.439
the lawyer was the same guy.

00:03:21.080 --> 00:03:21.840
Ruan Chen.

00:04:06.400 --> 00:04:07.240
Who are you?

00:04:10.439 --> 00:04:11.599
Who would've thought,

00:04:12.360 --> 00:04:13.719
Bro Mao's fake memorial hall

00:04:14.120 --> 00:04:16.240
would come in handy so soon.

00:04:17.959 --> 00:04:18.920
How much do you know?

00:04:19.360 --> 00:04:20.319
All I know is,

00:04:21.879 --> 00:04:22.879
you need money.

00:04:24.680 --> 00:04:25.959
You've been tailing me.

00:04:26.680 --> 00:04:27.879
It's business.

00:04:28.839 --> 00:04:29.839
With risky matters,

00:04:30.879 --> 00:04:32.279
you've got to be careful.

00:04:33.879 --> 00:04:35.360
Bro Mao's black money,

00:04:37.120 --> 00:04:38.279
he got it from you,

00:04:38.680 --> 00:04:39.360
didn't he?

00:04:39.879 --> 00:04:40.639
Not bad.

00:04:41.120 --> 00:04:42.360
I was just worrying

00:04:42.839 --> 00:04:44.680
if this pipeline could keep running.

00:04:45.519 --> 00:04:46.279
Lucky for me,

00:04:46.920 --> 00:04:48.360
you may be a little slow,

00:04:48.879 --> 00:04:50.079
but you'll do.

00:04:51.439 --> 00:04:52.600
I'm a businessman.

00:04:54.079 --> 00:04:56.120
I don't care if you're Bro Mao

00:04:56.680 --> 00:04:57.600
or

00:04:58.319 --> 00:04:59.079
Bro Xiao.

00:04:59.839 --> 00:05:01.399
As long as the deal goes through,

00:05:02.160 --> 00:05:03.399
anyone can be my Brother.

00:05:04.399 --> 00:05:05.399
And I need

00:05:05.759 --> 00:05:07.360
you to take Bro Mao's place,

00:05:07.680 --> 00:05:08.839
to keep this pipeline

00:05:09.319 --> 00:05:10.480
running.

00:05:27.759 --> 00:05:28.439
Since

00:05:29.199 --> 00:05:30.639
you recognize my value,

00:05:31.519 --> 00:05:32.240
then,

00:05:34.079 --> 00:05:35.920
can you do something for me?

00:05:36.879 --> 00:05:37.720
Let's hear it.

00:05:41.360 --> 00:05:42.399
Deliver something for me.

00:05:44.560 --> 00:05:45.680
What's your name?

00:05:46.920 --> 00:05:47.720
Ruan Chen.

00:06:25.800 --> 00:06:26.519
Da Tou.

00:06:27.160 --> 00:06:27.839
Luo Xiao.

00:06:28.079 --> 00:06:28.839
That address you had me find,

00:06:28.839 --> 00:06:30.240
Zhang Yuanshan's place, I got it.

00:06:30.399 --> 00:06:31.040
Sent it to you.

00:06:31.720 --> 00:06:32.879
Got the address.

00:06:34.079 --> 00:06:35.319
But there's one more thing.

00:06:36.040 --> 00:06:37.439
We've got to head over to A Min's.

00:06:38.360 --> 00:06:39.040
What for?

00:06:40.519 --> 00:06:41.600
You'll see when we get there.

00:06:43.000 --> 00:06:43.600
Alright.

00:06:43.759 --> 00:06:44.600
I'll come pick you up.

00:06:45.040 --> 00:06:45.680
No need.

00:06:46.319 --> 00:06:47.839
Just wait for me at A Min's place.

00:06:49.279 --> 00:06:50.600
You know where A Min is?

00:06:51.319 --> 00:06:51.800
Wait,

00:06:51.920 --> 00:06:53.079
Luo Xiao, what are you up to?

00:07:20.560 --> 00:07:21.319
Brother

00:07:22.360 --> 00:07:23.720
Take me to A Min

00:07:25.519 --> 00:07:26.120
Okay

00:07:56.480 --> 00:07:57.519
A Min, he's here

00:08:05.920 --> 00:08:07.680
Bro Mao told me to teach you a lesson

00:08:07.879 --> 00:08:09.279
So you learn to know your place

00:08:10.959 --> 00:08:12.720
Pin both of them down for me

00:08:14.439 --> 00:08:15.480
Take their stuff

00:08:22.800 --> 00:08:25.079
I thought you'd come to your senses

00:08:25.720 --> 00:08:27.759
Turns out you've Walked into a dead end

00:08:29.199 --> 00:08:30.600
Bro Mao was right after all

00:08:30.959 --> 00:08:32.519
A Min, you're trying to betray him

00:08:32.840 --> 00:08:33.919
A Min, you've gone insane

00:08:34.279 --> 00:08:35.559
Even if Bro Mao is gone

00:08:35.759 --> 00:08:36.519
What makes you think

00:08:36.639 --> 00:08:37.879
you can keep the company running?

00:08:41.519 --> 00:08:42.200
Talk

00:08:42.559 --> 00:08:43.720
Where did Bro Mao go?

00:08:53.759 --> 00:08:56.399
Wednesday, come pick them up if you're free.

00:08:59.440 --> 00:09:00.320
Mr. Big-Shot Lawyer,

00:09:01.799 --> 00:09:03.440
you definitely won't have time,

00:09:04.360 --> 00:09:06.279
'cause you're too busy digging your own grave.

00:09:07.759 --> 00:09:08.879
I've got time.

00:09:09.320 --> 00:09:10.759
I'll pick up Madam,

00:09:11.840 --> 00:09:13.159
and your little girl.

00:09:16.000 --> 00:09:16.679
A Min.

00:09:17.440 --> 00:09:18.159
I'll talk.

00:09:18.559 --> 00:09:19.399
I'll tell you

00:09:21.120 --> 00:09:22.120
Bro Mao's address.

00:09:22.480 --> 00:09:24.000
It's in the map on my phone.

00:09:29.360 --> 00:09:30.080
A Min.

00:09:30.600 --> 00:09:31.559
I've told you everything.

00:09:32.159 --> 00:09:33.360
I... I'm begging you.

00:09:33.679 --> 00:09:35.600
Please don't tell Bro Mao it was me.

00:09:35.840 --> 00:09:37.080
I've got a wife and kids.

00:09:37.360 --> 00:09:38.159
If Bro Mao finds out,

00:09:38.159 --> 00:09:39.480
he won't spare them.

00:09:39.720 --> 00:09:40.600
Please don't tell him.

00:09:40.799 --> 00:09:41.759
I'm begging you, A Min.

00:09:41.919 --> 00:09:42.720
Please.

00:09:48.200 --> 00:09:49.600
If you'd told the truth earlier,

00:09:50.120 --> 00:09:51.360
none of this would've happened.

00:09:52.720 --> 00:09:53.480
Let go.

00:10:00.080 --> 00:10:01.639
Da Tou.

00:10:03.240 --> 00:10:04.559
You're useless too.

00:10:06.039 --> 00:10:07.200
Look at the people you follow.

00:10:10.960 --> 00:10:11.559
A Min.

00:10:11.679 --> 00:10:12.480
The cops are here.

00:10:13.679 --> 00:10:14.600
Clean this place up.

00:10:14.679 --> 00:10:16.440
Toss these two out the back.

00:10:16.759 --> 00:10:17.399
Hurry.

00:10:21.799 --> 00:10:22.879
And their belongings.

00:10:23.000 --> 00:10:24.120
Dump them in the trash.

00:10:58.559 --> 00:10:59.919
Back when I was a lawyer,

00:11:00.559 --> 00:11:02.240
they said you had to have a nice watch.

00:11:04.279 --> 00:11:05.559
Don't need it anymore now.

00:11:08.240 --> 00:11:09.519
It'd be a pity to pawn it.

00:11:12.120 --> 00:11:12.960
Here, it's yours.

00:11:23.519 --> 00:11:24.960
Is Bro Mao's address real?

00:11:27.200 --> 00:11:28.440
If it is,

00:11:30.720 --> 00:11:31.720
what will A Min do?

00:11:47.559 --> 00:11:50.039
Tian Yong, the boss of Yizhan Technology, was killed.

00:11:50.440 --> 00:11:51.799
The former Yizhan Technology employee,

00:11:51.799 --> 00:11:53.200
Xin Qili, was sentenced.

00:11:53.639 --> 00:11:55.720
Ruan Chen, the former lawyer of Yizhan Technology,

00:11:56.000 --> 00:11:57.720
is now a Fortune Slip Interpreter at a temple.

00:11:58.320 --> 00:11:59.639
After Xin Qili got out of prison,

00:11:59.799 --> 00:12:00.720
he started moving goods.

00:12:01.320 --> 00:12:02.399
For his sister's illness,

00:12:02.600 --> 00:12:03.559
he went to draw a Fortune slip.

00:12:04.639 --> 00:12:05.360
And now Chen Yongjiang

00:12:05.360 --> 00:12:06.799
has killed Xin Qili.

00:12:09.360 --> 00:12:10.000
My head's spinning.

00:12:10.679 --> 00:12:12.600
These cases are too closely linked.

00:12:13.519 --> 00:12:15.159
I feel there's a tangled web behind it all.

00:12:16.679 --> 00:12:17.759
And this Ruan Chen,

00:12:17.799 --> 00:12:19.600
when he saw that Fortune slip,

00:12:20.240 --> 00:12:22.000
he deliberately hid from us

00:12:22.039 --> 00:12:24.200
the fact that they knew each other, right?

00:12:25.919 --> 00:12:26.840
This Feng Mao Company's

00:12:26.919 --> 00:12:28.679
Fund flow over the past six months...

00:12:29.320 --> 00:12:30.720
What? Anything unusual?

00:12:31.039 --> 00:12:31.879
Yes.

00:12:32.440 --> 00:12:33.960
Besides loan expenses,

00:12:34.240 --> 00:12:35.320
looking at these accounts,

00:12:35.399 --> 00:12:36.440
they deal with a company called

00:12:37.000 --> 00:12:38.519
Shengquan International Trade Company

00:12:38.600 --> 00:12:39.440
very frequently.

00:12:40.279 --> 00:12:41.279
The accounts are so complex,

00:12:41.279 --> 00:12:43.399
they're way beyond the normal range.

00:12:43.639 --> 00:12:45.559
The remarks on the transfer purposes

00:12:45.600 --> 00:12:46.360
are all kinds of things.

00:12:46.919 --> 00:12:48.559
Things like project promotion fees,

00:12:48.720 --> 00:12:51.080
temporary expenses, and outsourcing fees.

00:12:53.559 --> 00:12:55.039
Does this Shengquan Company have any

00:12:55.039 --> 00:12:56.039
financial dealings with Xin Qili?

00:12:56.799 --> 00:12:58.320
Based on what we know so far,

00:12:58.399 --> 00:12:59.039
no.

00:13:06.080 --> 00:13:07.679
Feng Mao Company's accounts are problematic.

00:13:08.080 --> 00:13:09.600
So if there are financial entanglements

00:13:09.600 --> 00:13:11.000
between Xin Qili and Chen Yongjiang,

00:13:11.480 --> 00:13:13.279
then the motive for murder isn't out in the open.

00:13:14.200 --> 00:13:15.799
It's hidden in these invisible accounts.

00:13:19.000 --> 00:13:19.600
Chief Zhang.

00:13:19.720 --> 00:13:20.639
Something's happened to Zhang Jiayuan.

00:13:21.039 --> 00:13:21.679
Let's go.

00:13:50.679 --> 00:13:51.159
Chief Zhang.

00:13:51.759 --> 00:13:53.159
Firefighters have finished their sweep.

00:13:53.639 --> 00:13:54.679
All hazards have been cleared.

00:13:54.799 --> 00:13:55.919
Fire department confirms the scene is safe.

00:13:56.559 --> 00:13:57.679
We can go in and investigate now.

00:14:02.080 --> 00:14:02.559
Chief Zhang.

00:14:02.639 --> 00:14:03.519
What's the scene look like?

00:14:04.000 --> 00:14:05.080
I checked the whole place.

00:14:05.200 --> 00:14:06.120
No casualties.

00:14:07.360 --> 00:14:08.879
Lucky no one was inside during the blast.

00:14:09.000 --> 00:14:09.799
Or it'd be a disaster.

00:14:12.200 --> 00:14:13.320
Blown up like this...

00:14:14.759 --> 00:14:16.200
The gas pipes on site are intact.

00:14:16.320 --> 00:14:17.480
The valves aren't damaged.

00:14:18.320 --> 00:14:19.320
But judging by the fire intensity

00:14:19.320 --> 00:14:20.600
and the blast marks on site,

00:14:20.759 --> 00:14:22.879
this far exceeds a typical gas explosion.

00:14:28.720 --> 00:14:29.639
Valves are fine.

00:14:31.399 --> 00:14:32.120
Where's the homeowner?

00:14:33.039 --> 00:14:33.519
Upstairs.

00:14:33.559 --> 00:14:34.480
Just finished giving his statement.

00:14:37.240 --> 00:14:37.960
Let's go see.

00:14:42.679 --> 00:14:43.559
Come on, get up. Chief Zhang.

00:14:44.399 --> 00:14:45.279
You're not hurt, are you?

00:14:45.399 --> 00:14:46.039
I'm fine.

00:14:46.200 --> 00:14:46.960
This is the homeowner.

00:14:47.320 --> 00:14:47.919
Hello.

00:14:48.519 --> 00:14:49.440
Let me explain something to you.

00:14:49.559 --> 00:14:51.279
Based on our investigation of the scene,

00:14:51.320 --> 00:14:52.360
this explosion at your home

00:14:52.559 --> 00:14:53.919
far exceeds what a gas leak

00:14:54.039 --> 00:14:56.279
or appliance explosion could cause.

00:14:57.960 --> 00:14:58.840
To put it bluntly,

00:14:59.080 --> 00:15:00.080
this could be deliberate.

00:15:01.080 --> 00:15:01.759
Who?

00:15:01.919 --> 00:15:02.639
Who'd want to blow me up?

00:15:02.799 --> 00:15:03.519
Who would want to kill me?

00:15:03.600 --> 00:15:04.360
Take your time.

00:15:04.559 --> 00:15:06.200
Where were you before the explosion?

00:15:08.360 --> 00:15:09.879
Last night someone called me out.

00:15:09.960 --> 00:15:10.919
I played cards all night.

00:15:11.240 --> 00:15:13.080
At dawn, I heard the explosion.

00:15:13.519 --> 00:15:15.440
I went out with others to check.

00:15:15.799 --> 00:15:17.480
That's when I saw my house was blown up.

00:15:18.919 --> 00:15:20.519
Have you offended anyone lately?

00:15:22.919 --> 00:15:23.840
A while back,

00:15:24.000 --> 00:15:25.720
my shop had some debt trouble.

00:15:26.080 --> 00:15:26.639
But...

00:15:26.759 --> 00:15:28.080
But it was just a small dispute.

00:15:28.240 --> 00:15:30.559
He wouldn't go this far, would he?

00:15:30.679 --> 00:15:32.080
Shop? What kind of shop?

00:15:32.360 --> 00:15:33.120
auto repair shop.

00:15:33.240 --> 00:15:34.200
A car repair shop.

00:15:35.039 --> 00:15:36.639
I owed some money I couldn't pay back.

00:15:36.879 --> 00:15:38.399
So they took the shop from me.

00:15:43.120 --> 00:15:43.799
Chief Zhang.

00:15:44.000 --> 00:15:45.440
This video's gone viral online.

00:16:04.639 --> 00:16:05.320
Eight dots.

00:16:05.879 --> 00:16:06.519
Pong.

00:16:07.960 --> 00:16:08.679
Your hand's so good.

00:16:14.519 --> 00:16:15.600
What's that supposed to mean?

00:16:18.919 --> 00:16:19.600
Madam.

00:16:20.080 --> 00:16:20.840
Listen,

00:16:21.039 --> 00:16:23.120
could we have a word in private?

00:16:26.440 --> 00:16:27.279
Let's stop here.

00:16:27.879 --> 00:16:29.080
I was one tile away.

00:16:29.399 --> 00:16:30.279
I'll cover it.

00:16:32.720 --> 00:16:33.559
You take a break too.

00:16:49.120 --> 00:16:51.080
Madam, sorry to bother you.

00:16:51.639 --> 00:16:52.559
Here's the thing.

00:16:55.080 --> 00:16:55.960
A while ago,

00:16:56.679 --> 00:16:58.679
some company funds got held up, right?

00:16:59.759 --> 00:17:01.759
A Min was skimming it on the side.

00:17:02.480 --> 00:17:05.039
Bro Mao found out, so he set a trap.

00:17:05.400 --> 00:17:06.920
He had me

00:17:07.279 --> 00:17:09.400
leak a fake address to test him.

00:17:09.759 --> 00:17:11.319
Didn't expect A Min...

00:17:11.720 --> 00:17:14.200
A Min really wants Bro Mao dead.

00:17:17.640 --> 00:17:19.039
A Min actually dared to skim money?

00:17:22.000 --> 00:17:22.680
Yeah.

00:17:23.480 --> 00:17:24.720
The day the Brothers held the big meeting,

00:17:24.960 --> 00:17:26.559
he brought a crew and crashed it.

00:17:26.799 --> 00:17:27.759
Called him out right to his face.

00:17:28.160 --> 00:17:29.160
Everyone heard it.

00:17:31.079 --> 00:17:32.720
Madam, here's how it is now.

00:17:33.720 --> 00:17:35.039
Bro Mao has eyes on him

00:17:35.160 --> 00:17:36.319
from all sides.

00:17:36.799 --> 00:17:37.960
As for the company,

00:17:38.319 --> 00:17:39.400
we need you to step in.

00:17:39.880 --> 00:17:40.799
As for these

00:17:41.160 --> 00:17:42.559
dirty riffraff,

00:17:42.799 --> 00:17:43.680
handle it.

00:17:52.200 --> 00:17:54.400
The fake address idea...

00:17:57.039 --> 00:17:58.200
That was yours, wasn't it?